    Dear Extreme AMOS,
    
        I am a little confused. I have been reading EA since it first came
    out, and was interested in advertising some of my best-selling games.
    In issue 1, you were charging absolutely ridiculous prices, which made
    me stop and look in other sources, as there was no way I was going to
    pay those kind of expenses. In the second issue, you said that Carl
    had gone from the team, and that the cost of placing adverts have
